/* Class = "UITextView"; text = "☆ \"Home\" tab\n・ MV advertisement displayed at the top of the screen\n・ Banner advertisement on each screen such as music playlist\n・ Full screen advertisements that sometimes appear when playing your favorite videos\n☆ Ranking tab\n・ MV advertisement displayed at the top of the screen\n・ MV advertisement displayed in related video list\n☆ \"Search\" tab\n・ MV advertisement displayed at the top of the screen\n・ MV advertisement displayed in related video list\n・ Full screen advertisements that sometimes appear during search\n☆ \"Options\" tab\n・ MV advertisement\n* All advertisements other than the “Text” tab are subject to deletion.\n--Please read below--\n!!Note!!\n・ You cannot delete videos that have advertisements inserted into the Youtube video itself.\n・ Advertising during scanning of the “Text” tab and translation function execution will be a burden to reduce server load.\nPlease note.\n\n◇ About “automatic continuous billing”\nIf the automatic renewal is not canceled within 24 hours, the contract period will be automatically renewed.\nYou will be charged for auto-renewal within 24 hours of expiration.\n\n◇ Confirmation and cancellation of contract period\nYou can check and cancel the contract period from Device Settings-> iTunes Store and App Store-> Tap Apple ID-> Display Apple ID-> Register-> musicA.\n* If there is no \"Register\", automatic update is not registered.\n\n◇ Restore purchase information\nWhen changing models, the purchase status can be restored free of charge.\nLog in to the device with the same Apple ID as when you purchased and press the “Restore from previous purchases” button.\n\n◇ Notes\n・ Cancellation for those who have been charged cannot be made by any other means.\n・ We do not accept cancellations for the current month.\n・ You will be charged via your iTunes account.\n\n◇ Terms of Use / Privacy Policy\n(Link: https://www.ios-app-develop.com/blank-8)\nWe do not provide personally identifiable information to third parties.\nPay close attention to the management of personal information and treat it as listed below.\n\n・ When supporting\nNo personally identifiable information will be sent.\nOnly the device type / OS version for analysis is included in the support email.\n\n・ Data analysis\nIn order to improve the convenience of the app, data analysis is performed when a problem occurs.\nData handled by developers here does not include personally identifiable data.\n\n◇ Disclaimer\nAlthough we provide support for problems and inconveniences as much as possible, the developer will not be liable for damages caused by users using this application."; ObjectID = "han-UX-fZu"; */
"han-UX-fZu.text" = "☆ \"Home\" tab\n・ MV advertisement displayed at the top of the screen\n・ Banner advertisement on each screen such as music playlist\n・ Full screen advertisements that sometimes appear when playing your favorite videos\n☆ Ranking tab\n・ MV advertisement displayed at the top of the screen\n・ MV advertisement displayed in related video list\n☆ \"Search\" tab\n・ MV advertisement displayed at the top of the screen\n・ MV advertisement displayed in related video list\n・ Full screen advertisements that sometimes appear during search\n☆ \"Options\" tab\n・ MV advertisement\n* All advertisements other than the “Text” tab are subject to deletion.\n--Please read below--\n!!Note!!\n・ You cannot delete videos that have advertisements inserted into the Youtube video itself.\n・ Advertising during scanning of the “Text” tab and translation function execution will be a burden to reduce server load.\nPlease note.\n\n◇ About “automatic continuous billing”\nIf the automatic renewal is not canceled within 24 hours, the contract period will be automatically renewed.\nYou will be charged for auto-renewal within 24 hours of expiration.\n\n◇ Confirmation and cancellation of contract period\nYou can check and cancel the contract period from Device Settings-> iTunes Store and App Store-> Tap Apple ID-> Display Apple ID-> Register-> musicA.\n* If there is no \"Register\", automatic update is not registered.\n\n◇ Restore purchase information\nWhen changing models, the purchase status can be restored free of charge.\nLog in to the device with the same Apple ID as when you purchased and press the “Restore from previous purchases” button.\n\n◇ Notes\n・ Cancellation for those who have been charged cannot be made by any other means.\n・ We do not accept cancellations for the current month.\n・ You will be charged via your iTunes account.\n\n◇ Terms of Use / Privacy Policy\n(Link: https://www.ios-app-develop.com/blank-8)\nWe do not provide personally identifiable information to third parties.\nPay close attention to the management of personal information and treat it as listed below.\n\n・ When supporting\nNo personally identifiable information will be sent.\nOnly the device type / OS version for analysis is included in the support email.\n\n・ Data analysis\nIn order to improve the convenience of the app, data analysis is performed when a problem occurs.\nData handled by developers here does not include personally identifiable data.\n\n◇ Disclaimer\nAlthough we provide support for problems and inconveniences as much as possible, the developer will not be liable for damages caused by users using this application.";

